    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="几何节点导论与概述"><a href="#几何节点导论与概述" class="headerlink" title="几何节点导论与概述"></a>几何节点导论与概述</h1><p>在使用几何节点修改器的时候需要将工作区切换到几何节点的编辑器</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lafew/picgo_xyz@main//img/image-20211123163226065.png" alt="image-20211123163226065"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lafew/picgo_xyz@main//img/image-20211123163355510.png" alt="image-20211123163355510"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lafew/picgo_xyz@main//img/image-20211123164010499.png" alt="image-20211123164010499"></p><p>参数化资产</p><p>日后摸索</p>]]></content>
    
    
